{"type": "article", "id": 22089, "title": "一本体育杂志应该拥有怎样的专属字体？", "description": "一家挺厉害的平面设计事务所的最新设计。", "date": "2016-02-10T08:00:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5584, "name": "ESPN"}, {"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 23250, "name": "体育杂志"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 23251, "name": "Hey"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 117, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152710OEqPKWBXV0TQRZHs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>最近，<a href=\"http://heystudio.es\">平面设计工作室 Hey Studio</a> 为 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ESPN_The_Magazine\">ESPN 的体育杂志 ESPN The Magazine</a> 设计了一款新字体。与之前的字体风格不同，新字体使用了切线和浅浮雕，以展现运动杂志的活力和个性。“ESPN 希望字体能充满活力，我们觉得浅浮雕能做到这一点。” Hey 的设计师们说。对一本杂志来说，好的字体应该是优雅有力的，而不应是笨重和傲慢，新字体基本上避免了这一点。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152700EgVPjsR0OC4vbh5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67403315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152701x4pwe7YmtUjd6ohR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67403315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152701Hdoqs2fJbZVGIAvx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67403315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152702gkIyrmuYxL4MjSZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67403315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152703TD0PeOQR6fH3NqhJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67403315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152704lin7WHFp8V6ArP5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67541436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://insider.espn.go.com/insider/espn-the-magazine/\">ESPN The Magazine</a> 是一本双周刊杂志，它由体育电视网 ESPN 创刊于 1998 年，这本杂志喜欢用轻松幽默的笔法介绍体育新闻，其中也不乏深度报道。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152705158M04RbXmJnlAVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.457\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p>Hey 则是一家位于西班牙巴塞罗那的平面设计公司，它成立于 2007 年，专注于品牌标志和插图设计。Hey 的设计师们偏爱使用几何形状和鲜艳的颜色，作品多富有视觉冲击力。2014 年，他们还开了一家网店。</p>\n<p>他们的客户包括 Apple, Monocle ，Vodafone, 华尔街日报、波特男士、企鹅兰登书屋等等。点开他们的网站（超链接在这篇文章第一句话，那个黄色下划线的部分），可以观赏到他们的作品大图，以下是他们的部分作品：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152705thKDBkO3jwYn2SeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152706kJmFTc3YP60Vqn9O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.447\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152707oyLZCasERiUJFM1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152707qE3w417P09KFjdsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152708i1KHMwu6VStjhfq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152709mlR9ckPEi1ShzWas.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152709dYyKvT1MklejwzEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.442\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152710nw5JcA20iuesB4VO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p>题图来源： <a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/hey-studio-espn-magazine-050216\">itsnicethat</a></p>\n\n"}